---
title: "Join :: Grateful Place"
---

#new-user
  %h2 Join Grateful Place

  %p Joining will let you write posts and comments.

  %form{:action => "/users", :method => "POST"}
    %table.input
      %tr
        %td.label
          %label{:for => "username"} Username
        %td#username
          %input{:name => "username", :type => "text"}
          .errors
      %tr
        %td.label
          %label{:for => "password"} Password
        %td#password
          %input{:name => "password", :type => "password"}
          .errors

      %tr
        %td.label
          %label{:for => "email"} Email
        %td#email
          %input{:name => "email", :type => "text"}
          .errors
    %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Join Grateful Place"}